shortDescriptions.default.value: This rechargeable headlamp can also be used with standard AAA batteries. It's light weight, comfortable, economic, flexible, and gives you 100 yards of visibility in pitch black. It features six light modes and allows you to easily recharge it with a USB or a standard wall plug in. The redesigned switch is easy to use, and is designed to work easily with gloves. It features two energy modes--Energy Saving Mode to help you optimize burning life, as well as Constant Mode that features continuous output.
descriptions.default.value:
This rechargeable headlamp can also be used with standard AAA batteries. It's light weight, comfortable, economic, flexible, and gives you 100 yards of visibility in pitch black. It features six light modes and allows you to easily recharge it with a USB or a standard wall plug in. The redesigned switch is easy to use, and is designed to work easily with gloves. It features two energy modes--Energy Saving Mode to help you optimize burning life, as well as Constant Mode that features continuous output.

Product Information & Features:

  • Catalog Page: 9927
  • 220 lumen power
  • Light modes: low power, mid power, high power, dim, blink, SOS
  • Can be battery operated (includes 2 AAA batteries)
  • Battery life: 5 hours
  • Comes with a standard wall charger and a USB charger
  • Flexible mount

Technical Specs:

  • Width: 3”
  • Length: 3”
  • Height: 3.5”
  • Depth: 2.5”
  • Weight: .8 lb.
category.default.title: Headlamps
